{"tid":1442651,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"攻佢721，派傳單點睇？","createTime":"2019-08-11T04:23:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T12:28:51.000Z","uid":301394,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"999bc6aec0a6eae201a5369ff6b267d09c1d67e4","tid":1442651,"uid":301394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:23:17.000Z","msg":"係其他 721 po 覆完即沉底<br />\n唯有自己po下。。。雖然應該都好快沉。。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 貼海報</span></strong></span><br />\n拜訪狗屋、民賤聯、支聯辦、正苦個陣唔好剩係屌佢老母<br />\n<br />\n貼啲支聯辦、正苦、民賤聯、克警、黑社會關係圖，加721事件文宣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">2. 地區派傳單、貼街招活動</span></strong></span><br />\n既然唔撚比遊行，不如搞派傳單？<br />\n- 將 721 警黑合作文宣係地區派<br />\n- 將&quot;民賤聯=&gt;克警=&gt;黑社會&quot; 講到11月區選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點睇？<br />\n<br />\n某程度上721可以幫到推向真普選，<br />\n&quot;721 = 正苦、克警、建制無能，唯有真普選先可以選到真正保護市民嘅人&quot;<br />\n咁嘅方向，唔知可唔可行？"},{"pid":"5e4d19b7db494ec6bbff4e475039ef9e387cea52","tid":1442651,"uid":301394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:24:21.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n求意見"},{"pid":"4e0c4c78c79ceb52a610f3c10865fa50f3d192b8","tid":1442651,"uid":266372,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:25:09.000Z","msg":"一定要咬住721黎講"},{"pid":"3d561fcacd5a033f177c76a78b8c6558615326ca","tid":1442651,"uid":301394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:25:15.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n求意見"},{"pid":"d5bb7a55b4bc06be6dab2f4b4e94f8671c417f76","tid":1442651,"uid":301394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e0c4c78c79ceb52a610f3c10865fa50f3d192b8","tid":1442651,"uid":266372,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:25:09.000Z","msg":"一定要咬住721黎講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:25:52.000Z","msg":"係！派傳單可唔可行？"},{"pid":"2557cfa8ef78991bb5f480df0af386166b7872b1","tid":1442651,"uid":20070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:26:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">針對警方無差別襲擊，標籤為<span style=\"color: red;\">國家恐怖主義武裝組織</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣核彈 - 為恐怖主義正名</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qMJqUur.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqMJqUur.jpg&h=36fb98e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n恐怖主義標籤係諸國用嚟打壓異己嘅手法，「國家當局可用以將政敵或其他對手非法化，從而使國家武裝部隊可理直氣壯地打擊敵人」，包括支那對新疆嘅打壓，都係以打擊恐怖主義為名，效果顯著。若果我地為警隊嘅恐怖主義正名，絕對係致命打擊警隊嘅合法性同認受性嘅方法。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">佢標籤我地做港獨，我地標籤返佢做「國家恐怖主義份子」 正名標籤警方為非法嘅武裝組織</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426058\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426058</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別襲擊製造恐怖氣氛絕對已經係恐怖主義！我地係嘅係要為警隊嘅行為正名！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">警隊失控無差別襲擊，係屬於國家恐怖主義嘅行為，已經超越「過度暴力」、「濫捕」同「濫用暴力」，依啲字眼淡化佢嘅「拐帶」、「恐怖襲擊」等非法行為，警隊嘅行為喺好多國家已經係可以定義為失去合法性啲武裝組織。<br />\n而且加上721恐襲同打後嘅黑警合作，有理由相信依個恐怖主義組織係跨越明同暗。現時警察喺民間嘅認受性極低，執法行動已變質，失去合法地執行職務嘅能力，街坊見到警察嘅武裝會產生恐懼感。恐怖主義管治已引起社會及國際極度不安。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fool1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/67630995_110432746967840_2331413204384612352_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQl4L1bx4RYkXXmGjLvLvV0mieI9WjtsALdVP9McHQyfw-djgsY6ZSsf-1vl88RayEY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fool1-1.fna&amp;oh=58b06b4db0bdb4fb6b665e75af38d026&amp;oe=5DD55B02\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fool1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F67630995_110432746967840_2331413204384612352_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQl4L1bx4RYkXXmGjLvLvV0mieI9WjtsALdVP9McHQyfw-djgsY6ZSsf-1vl88RayEY%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fool1-1.fna%26oh%3D58b06b4db0bdb4fb6b665e75af38d026%26oe%3D5DD55B02&h=2d15fa1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別化武襲擊！！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">[過期催淚彈][有圖] 毒到連眼都起水泡！！！！！麻煩全世界前線中線後線街坊啊婆啊伯！！戴靚少少既Gear唔該！！！！！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1436725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1436725</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">認同請聯署請分享</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fofficially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbU8LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=adc95295\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization</a><br />\n已有<span style=\"color: orange;\">44,418</span>/100,000個簽名（11 Aug 2019 at 10:56）<br />\n［白宮聯署］香港警察為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427701\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427701</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警黑合作 恐怖治國<br />\n警察本識 恐怖組織</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">槍炮化武 無差別襲擊<br />\n警黑勾結 武裝巴結<br />\nHKPF IS STATE TERRORIST!<br />\nNO STATE TERRORISM!<br />\nNO INDISCRIMINATE ATTACK!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n821守衛香港 反警黑恐怖治國 反恐大遊行/集會（未定）<br />\n821 - 元朗恐襲紀念日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1442294\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1442294</a>"},{"pid":"c3c8812f8dfb47c179e840ffa0f2ab8fad59a2f5","tid":1442651,"uid":301394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:26:03.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n求意見"},{"pid":"b4ffd894b4f9a4ec2b6f56d3f978bc7ad1e9b54d","tid":1442651,"uid":301394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:27:16.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n求意見"},{"pid":"4bde3dad6c1c37522d1b25c94ffaa6cfdeb13acf","tid":1442651,"uid":54228,"like":0,"di